  <guide>
    <section section_id="overview" title="Overview">
      <p>• Goal: reach at least 550 depth.</p>
      <p>• Tools: Pickaxe mines 1 block, Drill mines a full line, Bomb clears 5 wide and 5 tall, plus the four corner blocks.</p>
      <p>• You can find gems, extra tools, lucky chests (with durability), and event currency while mining.</p>
      <p>• Shop costs: Pickaxe 30, Drill 90, Bomb 90.</p>
      <p>• Tool usage: buy pickaxes; save drills/bombs for stone (2 hits) or clustered pickups, and use pickaxes for dirt (1 hit) or easy high value pickups.</p>
      <p>• Value rule: always open lucky chests, and skip low value treasures unless they pay back a pickaxe.</p>
      <p>• Dig down, buy pickaxes, ???, profit!</p>
    </section>
  </guide>
  <faq>
    <item faq_id="lucky_chests" question="How do lucky chests work?">
      <answer>
        <p>Lucky chests have limited durability. Each click gives tools, event currency, or gems until it runs out, then the chest disappears.</p>
        <p>It does not cost anything to open them, so always open them.</p>
      </answer>
    </item>
    <item faq_id="what_should_i_buy" question="What should I buy?">
      <answer>
        <p>From experience, it is best to only buy pickaxes and save drills/bombs for drops or task rewards.</p>
      </answer>
    </item>
    <item faq_id="depth_goal" question="What depth should I aim for?">
      <answer>
        <p>Reach at least 550 depth to get all rewards.</p>
      </answer>
    </item>
  </faq>
